# Weatherify

Weatherify is a simple weather application that fetches real-time weather data from the OpenWeatherMap API. It displays key information such as temperature, rainfall, humidity, wind speed, and more for a given city.

## Features

- Search for any city worldwide.
- Get real-time weather information.
- Responsive design for both desktop and mobile users.
- Data fetched from OpenWeatherMap API.

## Installation

To get started, clone the repository and install the dependencies:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/karthikeyan-dev3/weatherify.git
cd weatherify
npm install
